text.tspan: Share of male vs female employment in services, 2019
The horizontal axis shows female employment in services as a share of total female employment. The
vertical axis shows male employment in services as a share of total male employment. The services
sector consists of retail trade, restaurants and hotels; transport, storage, and communications; financing,
insurance, real estate, and business services; and community, social, and personal services.
Employment in services, female (% of female employment)
Employment in services, male (% of male employment)
Data source: International Labour Organization (via World Bank)
